### Test Recurring Patterns with Day Filters
### Login first to get token
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@tiffin.com",
  "password": "demo123"
}

### Save the accessToken from response above

### 1. Skip weekends - Only weekdays (Mon-Fri)
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-15",
  "endDate": "2024-01-31",
  "skipWeekends": true,
  "mealType": "LUNCH",
  "count": 1,
  "note": "Office lunch - weekdays only"
}

### 2. Specific days - Mon, Wed, Fri only (1=Mon, 3=Wed, 5=Fri)
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-02-01",
  "endDate": "2024-02-29",
  "daysOfWeek": [1, 3, 5],
  "mealType": "DINNER",
  "count": 2,
  "note": "Alternate day dinners"
}

### 3. Weekend meals only (0=Sunday, 6=Saturday)
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-01",
  "endDate": "2024-01-31",
  "daysOfWeek": [0, 6],
  "mealType": "BREAKFAST",
  "count": 1,
  "note": "Weekend breakfasts"
}

### 4. Tuesday and Thursday only (2=Tue, 4=Thu)
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-03-01",
  "endDate": "2024-03-31",
  "daysOfWeek": [2, 4],
  "mealType": "LUNCH",
  "count": 1,
  "note": "Gym days lunch"
}

### 5. All days (no filter) - same as before
POST http://localhost:3003/meals/bulk
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startDate": "2024-04-01",
  "endDate": "2024-04-07",
  "mealType": "DINNER",
  "count": 1,
  "note": "Every day dinner"
}

### 6. List meals to verify
GET http://localhost:3003/meals?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-04-30
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Dashboard summary
GET http://localhost:3003/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
